## Limitations
This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the scope of the sources reviewed. Some articles may not cover all aspects of the issue, and the perspectives included may not represent the full diversity of opinions on the topic. Additionally, the dynamic nature of political landscapes means that findings may evolve as new data becomes available.